{"tid":306827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[李嘉誠投資] VR公司總裁: 香港住屋細有利發展","createTime":"2017-07-03T00:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T05:56:30.000Z","uid":30561,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5bac82b575ad68e6f89fdecb7ebb5cf27e95d7b","tid":306827,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:38:04.000Z","msg":"虛擬實境（VR）成為近年熱門話題，最簡單一個紙盒加電話即可看到360度的影片。長和系主席李嘉誠早前就私人投資了美國一間「走動式VR」公司Nomadic。雖然正式產品要明年第一季才推出，但李嘉誠已率先將Nomadic引入香港。Nomadic行政總裁Doug Griffin認為，香港的住屋環境細小，反而更有利「走動式VR」發展。 <br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠旗下私人投資旗艦維港投資，早前領投Nomadic種子輪融資，金額近600萬美元（約4,680萬港元）。李嘉誠早前亦率先將Nomadic引入香港，於黃埔舉辦的「香港競XP」活動中讓市民免費試玩。 <br />\n<br />\nGriffin指出，香港屋住環境有限，要在家中享受VR遊戲有一定難度，如果單純是帶頭罩觀看360度的影片，或站著打機，都並非一個完整的VR體驗。他稱要有完整體驗，就需要走出屋外，相信類似的「走動式VR」在香港可以流行。"},{"pid":"b130ae6418a0bef9eeb18c280f39cea90effdde7","tid":306827,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:48:07.000Z","msg":"pokomon都俾車撞,vr會唔會跳樓"},{"pid":"96d798540bdf35e0e9f5c2d9e854d3705a924205","tid":306827,"uid":3109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pokomon都俾車撞,vr會唔會跳樓</blockquote><br />\n其實你有冇玩過vr<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f47cfda6cfb425b926e54c932832bd4f3ac5ede","tid":306827,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>pokomon都俾車撞,vr會唔會跳樓</blockquote><br />\n其實你有冇玩過vr<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼光淺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5abbed32b7d760973552974256f1d4397bddda","tid":306827,"uid":66975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>pokomon都俾車撞,vr會唔會跳樓</blockquote><br />\n其實你有冇玩過vr<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼光淺到<img src=\"/assets/fac